Package: SpectraQL
Title: MassQL support for Spectra
Version: 0.99.1
Description: The SpectraQL package adds support for the MassQL query language
    to Spectra objects. The Mass Spec Query Language MassQL was defined as a
    general query language to extract information from mass spectrometry data.
    This package provides the functionality to query Spectra objects from
    Bioconductor's Spectra package using MassQL.
